<div class="section-spacing">
    <div class="info-box">
        <h5>System Information</h5>
        <p><strong>Database:</strong> SQLite (LearnerManagementSystem.db)</p>
        <p><strong>Total Models:</strong> 17 entities with full CRUD operations</p>
        <p><strong>Workflow Roles:</strong> Student, Lecturer, Admin, Assessor Developer, Assessment Centre Admin, ETQA, QCTO</p>
        <p class="mb-0"><strong>Status:</strong> System operational and ready for use</p>
